[{"id":1016257,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"<p>听论坛一直有人说这个 FaceID 怎么怎么好用，工作需要买了一个 iphone,我才发现这东西有多难用</p>\n<ol>\n<li>识别率极差，侧躺基本不成功，早上睡眼朦胧基本不成功，趴在枕头上基本不成功，做菜放在桌面上我得特意把脸凑去过才能成功</li>\n<li>极度考验我拿手机的姿势，手指头得从最下面划上来，我拿上面不行（为啥不能改成安卓那种从哪往上扒拉都能开锁的设计呢）</li>\n<li>既然我都得扒拉那一下，为啥我不按个指纹呢，不太理解这个扒拉的逻辑</li>\n</ol>\n<p>说实话，用了 1 个月的 iphone ，很多时候我都想给他砸了，我感觉这个 6000 多的东西，不如我 2000 的安卓机。。\n接下来会发完整的吐槽贴。</p>\n<p>发这些是希望，iPhone 用户跳出他们的圈子，看看外面是啥样了。。。。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1016257","replies":205,"created_ts":1708241759,"created":"15:35:59","title":"新买的 iPhone 15，吐槽一下这个极其极其不好用的 FaceID","author":"IdJoel","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/IdJoel","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4e3/7418/196587_mini.png?m=1692777020"},{"id":1016095,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146","description":"<p>我没有</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1016095","replies":194,"created_ts":1708217218,"created":"08:46:58","title":"新年第一天，你们收到了开工红包没？","author":"dc2002007","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dc2002007","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aab9/b308/109575_mini.png?m=1706238791"},{"id":1016166,"node":"移民","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/immigration","node_image":"/static/img/node_default_mini.png","description":"年前跟中介交流过，雇主移民费用在 100 万人民币左右，可以分期五年支付，今年的目标就这个了，明年等到了加拿大给各位做汇报。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1016166","replies":135,"created_ts":1708227761,"created":"11:42:41","title":"今年的目标， Run 到加拿大","author":"Dosenf","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Dosenf","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/efa8/7dd3/288242_mini.png?m=1705300118"},{"id":1016281,"node":" WATCH","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/watch","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_mini.png?m=1633251402","description":"目前 S5 电池 88%<br /><br />睡前充满 100%<br />起床 85%<br 